    </questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>By inspection, \(x={@inspectedRoot@}\) is a root, so by the factor theorem, \({@x-inspectedRoot@}\) is a factor. Taking out this factor gives:</p><p>\[ p(x)=({@x-inspectedRoot@})({@quadraticTerm@}) \]</p><p>and factorising the quadratic,</p><p>\[ p(x)={@ta1@} \]<br></p>]]></text>
    </generalfeedback>
